m\": 1194, \"to\": 1203}, {\"ngram\": \"her opponent\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1223}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 24-year-old said: \\\"The disappointment comes a bit different this time round.\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1306, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The disappointment\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1267}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The last time I was disappointed with how I fenced, but now I am quite satisfied and I am more disappointed by the result.\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The last time\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1320}, {\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I gave everything that I had, I left it all on the piste, I did my best.\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1504, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"the piste\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not have done anything more different and that was the best I could do.\\\"\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1585, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1535}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She got off to a winning start atParis 2024,displaying composure as she edged out world No.\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1678, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a winning start\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1617}, {\"ngram\": \"atParis 2024,displaying composure\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1651}, {\"ngram\": \"world No\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1677}]}, {\"sentence\": \"46 Maria Calderon 15-14 in the table-of-64 bout and avenged her loss to the Peruvian at the 2023 world championships.\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1796, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1682, \"end\": 1687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Duchess_Maria_Nikolaevna_of_Russia\", \"score\": 0.9497777221587189, \"rank\": 0.05283320136537216, \"text\": \"Maria\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \