\"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2071}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the loss, Kiria will depart Paris with more confidence, more aware of her weaknesses and what she can bring to the table.\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2203, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2110, \"end\": 2115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.049851195468934e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the loss\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2090}, {\"ngram\": \"Kiria\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2097}, {\"ngram\": \"more confidence\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2136}, {\"ngram\": \"her weaknesses\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2166}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2202}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was in stark contrast to her mindset after the Tokyo Games, where she struggled to deal with the increased expectations that came with being an Olympian.\", \"from\": 2205, \"to\": 2363, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2354, \"end\": 2362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999827196, \"rank\": 1.7077774689346927e-11, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"stark contrast\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2231}, {\"ngram\": \"her mindset\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2246}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2268}, {\"ngram\": \"the increased expectations\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2329}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"All the other Olympians were doing top-eights, top-16s and I was top-64, (which made me think) do I even deserve to have the Olympian name if I can not live up to how the rest of them are doing?\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2501, \"end\": 2509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999827196, \"rank\": 1.7077774689346927e-11, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All the other Olympians\", \"from\": 2376, \"to\": 2399}, {\"ngram\": \"top-eights\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2421}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 2543, \"to\": 2551}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After a defeat, I felt like I did not really deserve it and then it kind of snowballs.\\\"\", \"from\": 2571, \"to\": 2658, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a defeat\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2585}, {\"ngram\": \"snowballs\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2656}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she believes she has grown since then, adding: \\\"I am more mature now in terms of how I think and the strategies I use, happy that I managed to do it better this time round.\", \"from\": 2660, \"to\": 2836, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2741}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Tokyo, my mind was all over the place.\", \"from\": 2837, \"to\": 2878, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2840, \"end\": 2845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999455506148841, \"rank\": 5.44469629883787e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my mind\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2854}, {\"ngram\": \"the place\", \"from\": 2868, \"to\": 2877}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you had asked me what I did wrong, I would have had no idea.\", \"from\": 2879, \"to\": 2942, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no idea\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time I am more conscious and mature.\\\"\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 2985, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her coach Henry Koh wa